FastQC: 

sudo apt-get install fastqc

TrimGalore: 

sudo apt-get install trim-galore

BWA:

sudo apt-get install bwa
bwa index /home/user/genome/Homo_sapiens_assembly38.fasta

Samtools: 

sudo apt-get install samtools

Bcftools: 

sudo apt-get install bcftools

SnpEff :

wget http://snpeff.sourceforge.net/snpEff_latest_core.zip
unzip snpEff_latest_core.zip -d /path/to/your/directory




